Package: beprepared
Type: Package
Title: BePrepared version: Predped combined with QVEmod
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-11-13
Author: person("Niels", 
               "Vanhasbroeck", 
               email = "niels.vanhasbroeck@gmail.com",
               comment = c(ORCID = 0000-0002-7423-0090))
Maintainer: Niels Vanhasbroeck <niels.vanhasbroeck@gmail.com>
Description: This package combines the M4MA pedestrian model with the QVE model of viral disease spread. The idea is to use this combination of models to simulate the spread of a virus in different types of environments under a specific set of behavioral interventions.
